sql:
SELECT COUNT(access_id) AS total_view_accesses
FROM access_logs
WHERE action = 'view';

SELECT AVG(median_salary) AS average_median_salary
FROM employment_data
WHERE year = 2014 AND education_level_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- Top 5 occupations for each year and education level; 
- Highest employment numbers refer to the 5 occupations with the largest employment_number for each year and education level; 
- Latest user access information refers to the most recent access date for each employment record.
